FAQ_TITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Explore the Cosmos: Your Questions Answered
FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Discover more about our revolutionary space exploration app
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: What features does your space app offer?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app provides real-time satellite tracking, space news updates, virtual reality space tours, and an interactive solar system map.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: Is the app suitable for both amateur and professional astronomers?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Absolutely! Our app caters to space enthusiasts of all levels, from curious beginners to seasoned professionals.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Can I use the app to plan stargazing sessions?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Yes! Our app includes a night sky planner with weather forecasts and optimal viewing times for celestial events.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Does the app offer educational content about space?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Indeed! We provide a wealth of educational resources, including articles, videos, and interactive lessons about astronomy and space exploration.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: How often is the space news content updated?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Our dedicated team ensures that space news is updated in real-time, bringing you the latest discoveries, mission updates, and cosmic events as they happen.
PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Explore the Cosmos: Your Questions Answered
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: What features does your space app offer?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app provides real-time satellite tracking, detailed planetary information, space news updates, and virtual space exploration experiences.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: Is the app suitable for both beginners and space enthusiasts?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Absolutely! Whether you're a curious novice or a seasoned astronomer, our app caters to all levels of space interest with adjustable content depth.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: Can I use the app for stargazing?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Yes! Our app includes a night sky map with augmented reality features, helping you identify constellations, planets, and satellites in real-time.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: How often is the space news updated?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: We provide daily updates on space missions, astronomical events, and scientific discoveries, ensuring you're always up-to-date with the latest cosmic happenings.
